transcript:

Customer: Ha.
Executive: Ha ji ha ji to main wo close kar de raha hun sir.
Customer: Kaun sa close? Hello?
Executive: Kya keh rahe hain sir?
Customer: Kya close ho raha hai?
Executive: Sir ticket ek ticket hoti hai na jaise ki aapne mujhe call kara aur maine aapki call nahi uthai. But kal hamari aapki google meet pe baat ho chuki thi right. Ab system mein wo call aapne kam kar diya bola tha vaise.
Customer: Ha ha wo to sir wo to kal hi ho gaya tha aap check bhi kar sakte hain.
Executive: Wo to ho gaya ab picture wala main Balaji ka aapko dekh ke bola tha sir vaise dal dena hai.
Customer: Ha ha sir usme che additional keywords add on hue hain. Theek aapne jo images di thi as per.
Executive: Kal hi kara hai sir aap dekh sakte ho.
Customer: Maine kal sham ko to dekha tha sir.
Executive: Sir kal sham mein update hone mein time lagta hai na sir. Turant hi uske specification theek uski aap pricing main abhi aapko list bhej dunga aap mujhe pricing de dijiyega. Theek.
Customer: Kyunki pricing main apni marzi se dal nahi sakta.
Executive: Pricing pricing sir price price.
Customer: Price to main apne hisab se dal dunga wo chinta mat karo.
Executive: Ha chaliye agar aap apne hisab se dal sakte hain to best and well hai.
Customer: Aap wo sab inquiry usme dekh ke dal do na inquiry nahi aata hai call nahi aata hai kyun aise ho raha hai.
Executive: Achcha theek hai.
Customer: Sorry hamare kal discussion isi cheez se related to hua tha sir ki aapka jo major sabse jyada jo buylead aur sabse jyada jo inquiry hai wo cast iron nahi hai sir usme performance mein aap dekh lijiye aur hamara dekh lijiye Balaji bhi hamara hi account hai.
Executive: To sir Balaji ka jo hai na wo all India unlimited cities ka hai aapka jo hai wo top sir kuch nahi hota hai trust chal raha tha tab bhi mera kam band nahi sir aapko main agar aap bolenge to main abhi aapko Balaji ka abhi abhi turant bhej deta hun aapko na Balaji ka data hi bhej deta hun rukiye.
Customer: Balaji ka data mere ko kya karna hai?
Executive: To vahi aap keh rahe ho na ki uske pass jyada inquiry uske pass business aa raha hai kyunki usne apne aap ko aap google karke dekh lo aap sirf google karke dekh lo Balaji ka jo naam hai wo all India.
Customer: Kam kiya usme kya kiya wo mere ko bhej dijiye na khali main check kar lunga.
Executive: Ha ha wo main bhej de raha hun aapko wo main bhej de raha hun aapko.
Customer: Ha theek hai.
Executive: Theek hai ha baki main ticket close kar raha hun sir aapke pass na ek wo jayega kya kehte hain mail jayega closer ka to please aap uska feedback de dijiyega theek hai.
Customer: Aisa to kuch aata nahi hai kya naya naya sab chalu hota hai.
Executive: Are sir ticket jab close hota hai jaise ticket jab khulta hai tab aapke pass feedback ke liye jata hai ki ha aapka ye baat chit ho gaya jo aapka miss call tha uski call back aapko aayi hai aur aapki baat chit ho gayi hai.
Customer: Miss call to maine ek hafte pehle bhi aapko chutti pe raha tab teen char bar nahi nahi chuttiyon wala consider nahi hota jis din working hota hai theek hai jab aapka kal working tha na jaise kal aapko main time bhi bata deta hun aapka kal kitne baje aapka miss call aaya wo bhi bata deta hun main aapne 11 baje call kiya tha na.
Executive: Ha unse to baat ho gayi thi sir.
Customer: Uska bhi call aaya tha wo 11 baje call kiya tha.
Executive: Achcha to mujhe lag raha hai ki 348 ek minute nahi nahi aap hi ka miss call hai 11:51 pe kal aapka miss call aaya tha.
Customer: Usko bhi aapne 12:30 baje call kiya.
Executive: Ha bilkul unko bhi call kara tha kyunki aapka call lag nahi raha tha aapne uthaya nahi tha maine call kiya tha to unko karna pada mujhe laga wo number bhi aap hi ka hai wo aapke bade bhaiya ka hai.
Customer: Ha achcha achcha chaliye theek hai ye bata diya aapne achcha hua hamara 11:51 pe aapka miss call aaya tha usse pehle hi hamari aapki baat ho chuki thi 11:49 pe maine call apna complete ho gaya tha theek apna lagbhag saat aath minute baat hua tha call pe usse pehle hamara 11:41 pe humne google meet ka link bhi maine aapko share kar diya tha to hamara pura baat chit jo tha wo google meet pe complete ho gaya tha fir aapka ek miss call yahan par pending reh gaya tha jo call back kal ho nahi pai hai na to system kehte hain ki agar koi bhi client ka agar aapke pass miss call pada hua hai to aap unko call back karke unse baat karo aap samajh rahe hain to wo priority ka ticket open ho jata hai main yahi aapko samjha raha hun to isliye wo ticket close hoga to aapke pass mail jayega official IndiaMART ki taraf se jayega ki sir ye ticket id hai aur ye aapka close hua hai ticket to aap is cheez pe satisfied mark kar sakte hain aisa.
Customer: Hmm.
Executive: Theek hai sir.
Customer: Theek hai.
Executive: Theek hai okay sir okay.
